      • R_ADJ_PVALS_SCOPE

        protected static final String R_ADJ_PVALS_SCOPE
        Config String property: "rStats.pAdjustScope" defines R p.adjust( n ) parameter. There are 4 supported options:
        1. "GLOBAL" n = number of all pVal tests for all fields and all taxonomy levels
        2. "ATTRIBUTE" n = number of all pVal tests for 1 field at all taxonomy levels
        3. "TAXA" n = number of all pVal tests for all fields at 1 taxonomy level
        4. "LOCAL" n = number of all pVal tests for 1 field at 1 taxonomy level
        See Also:
        Constant Field Values

      • R_PVAL_ADJ_METHOD

        protected static final String R_PVAL_ADJ_METHOD
        Config String property: "rStats.pAdjustMethod" defines p.adjust( method ) parameter. p.adjust.methods = c("holm", "hochberg", "hommel", "bonferroni", "BH", "BY", "fdr", "none")
        See Also:
        Constant Field Values
